<h1 align="center">💬 GUI Client-Server Chat Application</h1>

<p align="center">
  A Real-Time Chat Application built using Python, Socket Programming, Tkinter, and Multi-threading.
</p>

---

## 🚀 About The Project

This project is a GUI-based Client-Server Chat Application that enables real-time communication between a client and a server over a network.

The application uses Python sockets for communication and Tkinter for creating an interactive graphical user interface.

---

## ✨ Features

✅ Real-Time Messaging

✅ Client-Server Architecture

✅ Tkinter GUI Interface

✅ Multi-Threaded Communication

✅ Easy-to-Use Chat Window

✅ Fast and Lightweight

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

| Technology | Purpose |
|------------|----------|
| Python | Programming Language |
| Socket | Network Communication |
| Tkinter | GUI Development |
| Threading | Multiple Tasks Execution |

